      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm writing a paper on constitutional law and I'm stuck. Should religious organizations be allowed to opt-out of government mandates that conflict with their beliefs, or does that just undermine the secular nature of the state? Which side is actually more important for a healthy democracy?",
